{
  "texts": [
    "The digest of the data and the address of the symmetric key are recorded in a block on the blockchain and shared with the patient.",
    "An EMR is kept on the database as follows.",
    "{ ''p id '': ''1342'' ''firstname'': ''Ahmet'' ''lastname'': ''Yilmaz'' ''address'': ''address data'' ''emr'': { ''data'':''wetegbxfxygcerufjerufj674trsxgsgwr...'' ''fragments'':[''patient1342-disease2055-1'',''pa-tient1342-disease2055-2'',.. ''patient1342-disease2055n''] } } BlockchainWhen a patient's EMR is recorded in a distributed database, a digest of the EMR is recorded in a block on the blockchain.",
    "Although the blockchain is open to everyone, it is not possible to change the blocks.",
    "In this way, the digest of an EMR cannot be changed in any way."
